  <brief_title>A Survey of Factors Affecting an Early or Delayed Diagnosis of IgA Nephropathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Survey of Factors Affecting an Early or Delayed Diagnosis of IgA Nephropathy: an Observational Study</official_title>
